The paper deals with the topic of graph drawing, specifically monotone drawings of trees. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CG (Computational Geometry). The paper also involves algorithms and data structures, which suggests cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) as another likely category. The use of graphs and trees also suggests cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) as a possible category. The paper also involves graph theory and combinatorics, which could place it in cs.GR (Graph Theory) or cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
